    "title": "【修订】京东开放平台商家套利细则",
    "followRuleId": "1100364329796112384",
    "content": "<div class=\"mt-downmain\" style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between; line-height: 2; color: #999999; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-v-011e4cd2=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">尊敬的商家朋友们：</span></div><div id=\"floorcontent\" class=\"b-content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-v-011e4cd2=\"\"><div id=\"floorcontent\" class=\"b-content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-v-011e4cd2=\"\"><div class=\"o-mt\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\" data-v-196dd6b6=\"\"><p class=\"h-title\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: black; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, sans-serif;\">您好！</span></p></div><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">为维护京东开放平台商家的合规经营，提升消费者购物体验，对<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">《<span style=\"color: #3333ff;\"><a style=\"color: #3333ff;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=760061764627992576&amp;btype=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">京东开放平台商家套利细则</a></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; color: black;\">》</span> <span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\"><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">中违规定义及处理措施进行</span>修订</span>。</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">本次调整于2024年4月24日公示，于2024年5月1日起生效。</span></span></p><table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; border-color: #000000; border-style: solid; line-height: 2;\" border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><colgroup><col width=\"199\" /> <col span=\"2\" width=\"303\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center; background-color: #c00000; border: 1px solid #000000;\" width=\"199\" height=\"22\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>调整点</strong></span></td><td style=\"text-align: center; background-color: #c00000; border: 1px solid #000000;\" width=\"303\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>修订前</strong></span></td><td style=\"text-align: center; background-color: #c00000; border: 1px solid #000000;\" width=\"303\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>修订后</strong></span></td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid #000000;\" width=\"199\" height=\"178\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">违规场景名称及定义</span></td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" width=\"303\"><div><div><div data-v-ed192b8c=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>1.【违规定义】 <br />1.1营销套利：</strong>指商家不遵守诚信原则，实施谋私舞弊、虚假操作、套利行为（包括但不限于套取京东款项、京东优惠券、京豆、红包、佣金、垫付款及/或其他京东经营资源等）或实施其他侵害京东、客户、平台其他商家利益的行为。&nbsp;</span></div></div></div></td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" width=\"303\"><div><div><div data-v-ed192b8c=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>1.【违规定义】<br />1.1商家套利：</strong>指商家不遵守诚信原则，实施谋私舞弊、虚假操作、套利或套垫付款行为（包括但不限于套取京东款项、京东优惠券、京豆、红包、佣金、垫付款及/或其他京东经营资源等）或实施其他侵害京东、客户、平台其他商家利益的行为。&nbsp;</span></div></div></div></td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid #000000;\" width=\"199\" height=\"288\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">处理措施&nbsp;</span></td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" width=\"303\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>2.【处理措施】 </strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">2.5除上述处理措施外，京东有权追缴套利款项、关闭违规商家店铺，商家应向京东支付违约金壹佰万元，或按所涉商品销售额2倍支付违约金，二者从高适用。不足以弥补京东损失的，商家仍应赔偿京东全部损失。此外，视上述违规程度，京东有权冻结违规商家及其关联商家在京东的款项；商家行为构成犯罪的，京东有权向公安部门报案以进一步追究商家刑事责任。</span></td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" width=\"303\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>2.【处理措施】 </strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">2.5除上述处理措施外，京东有权追缴套利或套垫付款款项、关闭/停用价保等权益、关闭/停用工具、商品下架、全店限售、钱包冻结、限制服务市场交易、关闭违规商家店铺，商家应向京东支付违约金壹佰万元，或按所涉商品销售额2倍支付违约金，二者从高适用。不足以弥补京东损失的，商家仍应赔偿京东全部损失。此外，视上述违规程度，京东有权冻结违规商家及其关联商家在京东的款项；商家行为构成犯罪的，京东有权向公安部门报案以进一步追究商家刑事责任。</span></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"table\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: auto; line-height: 2;\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"l-content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 20px; min-height: 500px; color: #666666; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; line-height: 2;\" data-v-196dd6b6=\"\"><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: right; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\">京东</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: right; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\">2024年4月24日</span></p></div></div></div>",
